6. Reflection

Enterprise systems grow larger and more complex over time. Initially, configuration tools like Flow Builder are enough for simple business processes. However, organizations eventually require advanced automation, integrations, calculations, and custom logic.

Programming using Apex becomes important because it provides:

Greater flexibility
Better scalability
Advanced integrations
Complex business logic handling
Improved automation capabilities
